^*Bhondo717:^*N Good playing aggie. A club was a good lead. Either the 10 or low is fine. moe has 4, and it is the unbid suit. Now, let us review aggie's responsibilities as responder. Before I forget, I have a good tutorial on this subject, called "Introduction to Constructive Bidding". suggest you download it from my web site at

